  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为SJF非抢占式调度算法的第一个阶段画一个甘特图，时间范围是0到15秒。这个场景有四个进程P1、P2、P3、P4，需要展示CPU执行和I/O操作的重叠关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "0 15s",
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，SJF非抢占式意味着一旦进程开始执行就不能被中断。我需要确认一下：这个图要分几个section？CPU和I/O分开显示吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "secti",
        "cpu",
        "io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，分成两个section：CPU和I/O。CPU部分显示进程实际执行的时间段，I/O部分显示每个进程发起I/O请求后的等待时间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "secti",
        "cpu",
        "io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把整体框架搭起来。标题用\"Planificación SJF Non-Preemptive - Parte 1 (0-15s)\"，时间格式用纯数字秒数，坐标轴显示秒。这样符合要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "datef",
        "axisf",
        "0 15s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。现在说具体调度顺序：P1最先到达，执行0到5秒。P1完成后发起I/O，同时CPU空闲检查就绪队列，P4的突发时间最短，所以P4接着执行5到7秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "0 5",
        "p1 io",
        "p4",
        "5 7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我在CPU section添加了P1(0-5)和P4(5-7)两个任务条，都用active状态标记。I/O section加上P1_IO(5-7)，用crit标记表示这是关键路径上的等待。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu1",
        "cpu2",
        "io1",
        "active",
        "crit",
        "0 5",
        "5 7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来P4在7秒完成，同时P1的I/O也刚好结束。但P4又需要I/O，所以CPU交给下一个最短作业P2，执行7到10秒。P4去做I/O，7到10秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p4 io",
        "p2",
        "7 10"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：CPU section的P2(7-10)，I/O section的P4_IO(7-10)。现在CPU和I/O都有并行活动了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu3",
        "io2",
        "7 10"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "到10秒时，P2完成，P4的I/O也完成。但P4已经执行过一次了，现在就绪队列里有P3和P4。P3的突发时间更短，所以P3先执行10到14秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3",
        "10 14",
        "p4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "P3执行期间，P2的I/O什么时候开始？P2在10秒完成CPU执行，应该立即进入I/O吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2 io",
        "10 11"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，P2的I/O很短，只有10到11秒一秒时间。这个要标出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2 io",
        "10 11"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了：CPU section的P3(10-14)，I/O section的P2_IO(10-11)。P2的I/O确实很短，只有1秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu4",
        "io3",
        "10 14",
        "10 11"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后，P3在14秒完成，P4的I/O其实10秒就完成了但一直在等CPU。所以14到15秒P4执行最后1秒完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p4",
        "14 15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，添加了P4(14-15)到CPU section。这样P4分成了两段执行：5-7和14-15，中间7-10在做I/O。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu5",
        "14 15",
        "5 7",
        "7 10"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我检查一下时间。P4的I/O是7-10，P3是10-14，P4第二段是14-15。那P4从10秒I/O完成到14秒，等了4秒？这符合非抢占式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p4 io",
        "p4",
        "10 14",
        "preemptive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "符合的，非抢占式指的是CPU执行期间不能被中断，但I/O完成后进程回到就绪队列等待，这是正常的。P4确实等了4秒才再次获得CPU。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "preemptive",
        "p4",
        "10 14"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那P3有没有I/O？这个场景里P3和P4的第二段I/O我们暂时不画，因为只展示0-15秒，而且parte 1聚焦在核心调度过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3",
        "p4 io",
        "parte",
        "0 15s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，当前图中I/O section只有P1_IO、P4_IO、P2_IO三个任务，P3没有I/O活动。这样15秒内所有进程都完成了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "io1",
        "io2",
        "io3",
        "p1 io",
        "p2 io",
        "p4 io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，P1的I/O是5-7，但P1之后还有CPU执行吗？让我重新理一下——实际上P1在5秒完成CPU和I/O后应该还有第二段，但0-15秒内我们只画到I/O结束，因为P1的第二段在15秒之后。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p1 io",
        "5 7",
        "0 15s"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以P1_IO(5-7)之后没有继续画，因为parte 1只覆盖0-15秒，P1的后续执行超出范围。当前图示是正确的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1 io",
        "5 7",
        "parte",
        "0 15s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，最终确认一下时间轴：CPU section是P1(0-5)、P4(5-7)、P2(7-10)、P3(10-14)、P4(14-15)，I/O section对应三个关键等待期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu1",
        "cpu2",
        "cpu3",
        "cpu4",
        "cpu5",
        "io1",
        "io2",
        "io3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部核对完毕。甘特图已最终确定，两个section、五个CPU任务条、三个I/O任务条，时间范围0-15秒，所有active和crit状态标记正确。",
